      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:1",
      "text": "ܐܢ ܒܟܠ ܠܫܢ ܕܒܢܝܢܫܐ ܐܡܠܠ ܘܒܕܡܠܐܟܐ ܘܚܘܒܐ ܠܐ ܢܗܘܐ ܒܝ ܗܘܝܬ ܠܝ ܢܚܫܐ ܕܙܐܡ ܐܘ ܨܨܠܐ ܕܝܗܒ ܩܠܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.2",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:2",
      "text": "ܘܐܢ ܬܗܘܐ ܒܝ ܢܒܝܘܬܐ ܘܐܕܥ ܐܪܙܐ ܟܠܗܘܢ ܘܟܠܗ ܝܕܥܬܐ ܘܐܢ ܬܗܘܐ ܒܝ ܟܠܗ ܗܝܡܢܘܬܐ ܐܝܟܢܐ ܕܛܘܪܐ ܐܫܢܐ ܘܚܘܒܐ ܠܝܬ ܒܝ ܠܐ ܗܘܝܬ ܡܕܡ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.3",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:3",
      "text": "ܘܐܢ ܐܘܟܠ ܟܠ ܕܐܝܬ ܠܝ ܠܡܤܟܢܐ ܘܐܢ ܐܫܠܡ ܦܓܪܝ ܕܢܐܩܕ ܘܚܘܒܐ ܠܐ ܢܗܘܐ ܒܝ ܡܕܡ ܠܐ ܝܬܪ ܐܢܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.4",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:4",
      "text": "ܚܘܒܐ ܢܓܝܪܐ ܗܝ ܪܘܚܗ ܘܒܤܝܡ ܚܘܒܐ ܠܐ ܚܤܡ ܚܘܒܐ ܠܐ ܡܫܬܓܫ ܘܠܐ ܡܬܚܬܪ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.5",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:5",
      "text": "ܘܠܐ ܤܥܪ ܕܒܗܬܬܐ ܘܠܐ ܒܥܐ ܕܝܠܗ ܘܠܐ ܡܬܬܦܝܪ ܘܠܐ ܡܬܪܥܐ ܕܒܝܫ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.6",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:6",
      "text": "ܠܐ ܚܕܐ ܒܥܘܠܐ ܐܠܐ ܚܕܐ ܒܩܘܫܬܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.7",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:7",
      "text": "ܟܠ ܡܕܡ ܡܤܝܒܪ ܟܠܡܕܡ ܡܗܝܡܢ ܟܠ ܡܤܒܪ ܟܠ ܤܒܠ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.8",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:8",
      "text": "ܚܘܒܐ ܡܡܬܘܡ ܠܐ ܢܦܠ ܢܒܝܘܬܐ ܓܝܪ ܢܬܒܛܠܢ ܘܠܫܢܐ ܢܫܬܬܩܘܢ ܘܝܕܥܬܐ ܬܬܒܛܠ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.9",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:9",
      "text": "ܩܠܝܠ ܗܘ ܓܝܪ ܡܢ ܤܓܝ ܝܕܥܝܢܢ ܘܩܠܝܠ ܡܢ ܤܓܝ ܡܬܢܒܝܢܢ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.10",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:10",
      "text": "ܐܡܬܝ ܕܝܢ ܕܬܐܬܐ ܓܡܝܪܘܬܐ ܗܝܕܝܢ ܢܬܒܛܠ ܗܘ ܡܕܡ ܕܩܠܝܠ ܗܘܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.11",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:11",
      "text": "ܟܕ ܝܠܘܕܐ ܗܘܝܬ ܐܝܟ ܝܠܘܕܐ ܡܡܠܠ ܗܘܝܬ ܘܐܝܟ ܝܠܘܕܐ ܡܬܪܥܐ ܗܘܝܬ ܘܐܝܟ ܝܠܘܕܐ ܡܬܚܫܒ ܗܘܝܬ ܟܕ ܗܘܝܬ ܕܝܢ ܓܒܪܐ ܒܛܠܬ ܗܠܝܢ ܕܛܠܝܘܬܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.12",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 13,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 13:12",
      "text": "ܗܫܐ ܐܝܟ ܕܒܡܚܙܝܬܐ ܚܙܝܢܢ ܒܦܠܐܬܐ ܗܝܕܝܢ ܕܝܢ ܐܦܝܢ ܠܘܩܒܠ ܐܦܝܢ ܗܫܐ ܝܕܥ ܐܢܐ ܩܠܝܠ ܡܢ ܤܓܝ ܗܝܕܝܢ ܕܝܢ ܐܕܥ ܐܝܟ ܡܐ ܕܐܬܝܕܥܬ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.13.13",
